  "description": {
    "zh": "好了，雇佣兵，你又一次证明了自己的能力。真遗憾这片区域可能会埋没如此巨大的潜力。\n\n不过，这项行动还有最后一个任务需要你帮忙，所以仔细听好了。\n\n我们需要在疗养院的某些特定地点藏一些物品。我会提供一份清单，上面列出了需要藏匿物品的房间和物品。\n\n记住，这些房间可能是上锁的或难以进入的，所以带上钥匙。我可以提供所需的物品，但千万别弄丢了。",
    "en": "Alright Mercenary, you have proven yourself worthy once again, shame what potential might get lost in this region.\n\nAnyway, there is still one last task for this operation that I need your help with, so better listen up.\nWe need to stash a couple of things somewhere in the sanatorium, the places have to be very specific but I can provide you with a list of all the rooms and items that you need to stash in there.\n\nKeep in mind that some of these rooms are probably locked or hard to get to, so bring keys.\nI can also give you the required items, but do not lose them."
  },
